snippet.textDisplay: @Jielin Zhou Yes, Taiwan is more realistic about omicron than China. China is "fighting the last war", trying to eradicate Covid as they almost succeeded in doing in Wuhan in 2020. But omicron is a different variant, calling for different tactics. Complete eradication of this much more infectious variant is impossible. Greater reliance on vaccination is key. But Chinese vaccines aren't very effective, and the elderly population has avoided taking them.
